{"tid":2316544,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史幻想題","createTime":"2020-12-08T03:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T07:57:44.000Z","uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c36474ab6765c53979ad88a45910dec5ae3e2919","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"見到今日咁嘅香港：濫捕異見人士、隨意羅織罪名、任意凍結私人財產、防疫漏洞百出&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n請問有歷史以嚟，邊個時期、邊個地方嘅人民（唔計統治階層）先算最幸福嘅呢？點解呢？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"7a3c98dbf90504cc2343e028646ff7853f8d6258","tid":2316544,"uid":131617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"過咗嚟香港嘅鬼佬 (任何年代)"},{"pid":"5a2bdb68360e9b3a14fba272c08fa83bc308c93d","tid":2316544,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"打開本世史書會見到近個百幾年都唔少戰爭 但2戰之後會影響到西歐同美國平民既就少啲 頂多係做下核戰演習"},{"pid":"261b86cdf2aafaa56d91b40fb7e350c67ee2a942","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3c98dbf90504cc2343e028646ff7853f8d6258","tid":2316544,"uid":131617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"過咗嚟香港嘅鬼佬 (任何年代)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:24:17.000Z","msg":"希望從一般普羅大眾角度去睇，從而考慮點樣先算一個健全嘅制度，同埋點先可以達到呢個目標。<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬喺香港不嬲都係半個特權階級，無計&hellip;"},{"pid":"4385cd8cfe70750a39c28d8d855c53d7638b1c4b","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"我拋下磚&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n七十年代至九七年嘅香港算唔算？<br />\n<br />\n自由度高、貧富懸殊慢慢改善緊（唔計九十年代）、教育算普及化、少量基本社會福利、貪污度唔算高&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n諗返轉頭，有幸enjoy過少少&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n今日&hellip;唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32f1a4d63acaecd5b4eeacd3bcb25417e9f0259","tid":2316544,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"美國八九十年代<br />\n歐洲二千年頭"},{"pid":"59f50de220c3cfed637f625037530de8efe8965a","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"又諗下另外幾個歷史環境：<br />\n<br />\n民國時期（1920－1930）嘅廣東或者上海<br />\n<br />\n明治維新至1920期間嘅日本（會唔會好銀魂個背景咁？）<br />\n<br />\n納粹當權前嘅德國<br />\n<br />\n內戰後至第一次世界大戰前嘅美國？"},{"pid":"e6f647f0d6a6d96c39b865bfec9e163d0f4a66b8","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"食晏自推，1/10"},{"pid":"8f7d93ea0690e22c0aec906e66ed4062ff9fcd2b","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"食完晏再自推2/10"},{"pid":"1a19842609b59c7b5a7b539a97ba63da07fa9b6b","tid":2316544,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"7,80年代嘅香港 日本<br />\n魚翅撈飯 金箔麵"},{"pid":"fc3c1d9050b06fa35df7b5d85bccf2888313c8d6","tid":2316544,"uid":315372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f50de220c3cfed637f625037530de8efe8965a","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"又諗下另外幾個歷史環境：<br />\n<br />\n民國時期（1920－1930）嘅廣東或者上海<br />\n<br />\n明治維新至1920期間嘅日本（會唔會好銀魂個背景咁？）<br />\n<br />\n納粹當權前嘅德國<br />\n<br />\n內戰後至第一次世界大戰前嘅美國？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"德國納粹黨上台之前經濟好差喎 通脹高到pk"},{"pid":"fd1465164d26a83929d9d84353563008b13ddbfe","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"放工推一推3/10<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"02769dcde66cc1e12f017146aa268b85574542dc","tid":2316544,"uid":366281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f50de220c3cfed637f625037530de8efe8965a","tid":2316544,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"又諗下另外幾個歷史環境：<br />\n<br />\n民國時期（1920－1930）嘅廣東或者上海<br />\n<br />\n明治維新至1920期間嘅日本（會唔會好銀魂個背景咁？）<br />\n<br />\n納粹當權前嘅德國<br />\n<br />\n內戰後至第一次世界大戰前嘅美國？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:59:05.000Z","msg"